==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: By candle-light at the third watch, up with the chickens at the fifth watch.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: sān gēng dēng hŭo wŭ gēng jī

===Idiom===
'''[[三更]][[灯火]][[五更]][[鸡]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# To [[burn the midnight oil]], only to get up at the crack of dawn.
# To work long hours.
# to [[burn one's candle at both ends]].

#: ''[[就是]][[这样]][[的]][[一道]][[槛]]，[[让]][[众多]][[的]][[学子]]“'''三更灯火五更鸡'''”，[[让]][[众多]][[的]][[学校]][[加]][[课]][[补]][[课]][[取消]][[节]][[假日]].'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[就是]][[這樣]][[的]][[一道]][[檻]]，[[讓]][[眾多]][[的]][[學子]]“'''三更燈火五更雞'''”，[[讓]][[眾多]][[的]][[學校]][[加]][[課]][[補]][[課]][[取消]][[節]][[假日]].'' (Traditional Chinese)

===Alternate forms===
[[三更]][[燈火]][[五更]][[雞]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

